      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet kas tohs Jaunekts ar Stohperni noschandibs/ tee arrt ne schehlohs tohs Behrnus eekſch Mahtes Meeſahm/ winno Azz tohs Behrnus ne faudschs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta buhs Babels to Walſtibo Glihtuims/ tas Skaistums un ta Lepniba to Kaldeero/ itt ka Deews Sodomu un Gomorru irr apgahſis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tur muhſcham neweens dſihwohs/ tur arrt neweens mahfohs lihds Raddu Raddeim/ ir tee Arabexi tur ne apmetriſees/ nedbs tee Ganni tur apguſieces.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Zijſin tur apguſieces/ un winno Nammi taps ar Ojim peepilditi/ un tur turreſces junnt Strauſi/ un Johdi tur lehkahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Palladas uhpehs winnas atſtahtds Nammds/ un Pukti eerſch tahm staistahm Pillim/ un winnas Laiks irr jniv tuwu nahzis/ un winnas Deenas ne kawefers.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS apſcheh loſees pahr Jehkabu/ un Israelu wehl tswehlehs/ un weddibs tohſawa Semmē. Un Swechiueeki apbeedrnuſees ar teem/ un peekehrfees tam Jehkaba Rainmanz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tahs Tantas tohs peehrems/ un weddibs tohs us fa wahn Weetahm/ un tas Israelta Nauns eemantohs tahs eekſchtas KUNGA Semmes par Kal\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "peem un Kalponehim. Un turrehg tohs Zeetuma/ kas winnuſbij Zeetuma turrejſchi/ un wal dihs pahr fatweem Dsinnejeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XIV. Nodalla. Cepreezinachana preekſch teem Judu laudimkas atkat fara Semme nahks/ un arriohs Paganus par Tizzibas Beedreem dabbuhs:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Papreekschſluddinaſchana no tahs breefamigas Bohja Eſchanas ta Babeles Lehnika: 3. Ka arri ta Nehnina no Affirijas Saneriba: 24.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N tai Deend/ kad tasUKUNGS tew Duſteſchann dohs no tawahmSahpehn/ un no tawas Iebatles/ un no tahs geuhtas Kalpoſchanas/ ar ko winnt tew likufcht kalvoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad walkaſt tur fcho falka mo Wahrdu prett to Kehnimno Babets/ un fozzifti: Ka irrtas Dſinrejs mittejees? ka irr tasSelta Metteklis va Gallam?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS irr to Besdeewigo Siſlt falausijs/ to Walditaju Rihefit.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "kas tohs Landis mozijaar Dufmahni/ ar weenu neuhtejamu Metzibu/ kas ar Bahrijibu prett tahm Tantahm wal dija/ tas tobp waiahts/ ka neweens fo warr afekaweht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiffa Semme duſs untrekluſſit/ tee ribbeht riib ar Gawtleſchamit.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir tahs Preedes preezafahspahr tewi/ un tee Bedra Kobfi no Libbauns/(un faffx:) NotaLaika ka tu feimē quilī/ ne ustakhpj neweens/kas muhs nozebrt.\n"
    }
